<m0>Clean up<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 4.16 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>Fantasy Fest?<ql>
<m4>   LINE 2 IS .17 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>Dream on<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 3 IS 3.08 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.212 INCHES<m2><ql>
